#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Download Khan Academy
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This script allow you do download a entire course from Khan Academy directly from
the website. So you can have a updated course without trouble.

You can enable convertion too. So after download the course ir will convert the
videos to a desired format.


#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Software Requeriments:
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - python 3.x
    - get_flash_video 1.24
    - Linux shell
    - ffmpeg ( For convertion )



#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Using
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1 - ) Open the file index and delete the unwanted courses. All courses left in 
the file will be downloaded.

2 - ) You have to enable convert files if you want it. To do it just put True 
instead False in the variable convertVideos in the beginning of the file 
downloadkhanacademy.py
 
3 - ) Execute downloadkhanacademy.py giving the following command on the shell:
./downloadkhanacademy.py

4 - ) The program will open the file index and download the courses in there.


If one or more videos fail to download the script will retry to get them.

You can copy the file indexFULL to index so you can have all courses to choose.



